      { type: "fitb", text: "The key difference between an entrepreneur and a manager is that entrepreneurs ___ risk, while managers administer within established systems.", answer: "bear", explanation: "Entrepreneurs commit their own resources under conditions of uncertainty — risk-bearing is their defining function." }
